Get prospecting activity history for a lead (emails sent, calls made, status changes, notes). Each entry is `{type, date}`; older activities are trimmed by `count` (max 100, default 50).

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} to avoid redundant outreach and understand where this lead is in the sales process.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} when leadbay_research_lead has already been called — it includes recent prospecting actions in its engagement block.
